		<i>It's 3 a.m. and you just woke up from <br />this incredible dream...</i>
	</p>

	<div class="row margin-top hidden-phone visible-desktop">
		<div class="span6">
			<p class="font-hero">
				Capture your most memorable dreams <br />-in words and images- <br />and turn them into life memories.
			</p>
